BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Burnout is not just being tired. It is a state of chronic physical, emotional, and mental) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (exhaustion caused by prolonged stress. It affects your health, relationships, identity,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (and quality of life. Recovery is possible, but it requires intentional changes - not just) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (a vacation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (This workbook guides you through understanding your burnout, assessing its severity, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 610.2 Td (building a personalized recovery plan that restores your energy, purpose, and joy.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
