BT /F2 11 Tf 54 652.2 Td (1. Exhaustion \(Physical and Emotional\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 636.2 Td (- Feeling drained, depleted, unable to recover with rest) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 622.2 Td (- Chronic fatigue that sleep doesn't fix) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 608.2 Td (- Getting sick more often \(immune suppression\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.2 Td (- Physical symptoms: headaches, muscle tension, digestive issues) Tj ET
