BT /F1 10 Tf 54 560.2 Td (- Feeling detached, numb, or negative) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 546.2 Td (- Loss of caring about work or responsibilities) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 532.2 Td (- Irritability and impatience with others) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 518.2 Td (- Withdrawal from colleagues, friends, and family) Tj ET
