BT /F1 10 Tf 54 484.2 Td (- Feeling incompetent despite past achievements) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 470.2 Td (- Inability to concentrate or produce quality work) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 456.2 Td (- Self-doubt and imposter syndrome intensified) Tj ET
