BT /F2 12 Tf 54 412.4 Td (Burnout vs. Depression vs. Regular Stress) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 394.4 Td (Stress: You feel overwhelmed but engaged. Recovery happens with rest.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 380.4 Td (Burnout: You feel empty and beyond caring. Rest alone doesn't help.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 366.4 Td (Depression: Pervasive hopelessness affecting all life areas. Burnout can trigger) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 352.4 Td (depression - seek help if hopelessness persists.) Tj ET
