BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 3: Cortisol & Stress Management) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Understanding Cortisol) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (Cortisol is your primary stress hormone. In burnout, the cortisol system becomes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (dysregulated - often high at night \(can't sleep\) and low in the morning \(can't wake) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.2 Td (up/function\). This is HPA axis dysfunction.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 600.4 Td (Healthy Cortisol Rhythm) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 584.4 Td (- Highest in morning \(helps you wake up and feel alert\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 570.4 Td (- Gradually decreases throughout the day) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 556.4 Td (- Lowest at night \(allows sleep\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 538.4 Td (Burnout Cortisol Pattern) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 522.4 Td (- Low in morning \(exhaustion, can't get going\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 508.4 Td (- Spikes at random times \(anxiety, panic\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 494.4 Td (- Elevated at night \(insomnia, wired-but-tired\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 464.6 Td (Cortisol Recovery Protocol) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 442.6 Td (Morning \(Support natural cortisol rise\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 426.6 Td (- Wake at consistent time) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 412.6 Td (- Sunlight within 30 minutes \(sets cortisol clock\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 398.6 Td (- Protein-rich breakfast \(stabilizes blood sugar\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 384.6 Td (- Avoid checking phone/email for first hour) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 370.6 Td (- Gentle movement \(walk, stretch\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 352.6 Td (Afternoon \(Prevent cortisol spike\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 336.6 Td (- Eat regular meals \(blood sugar drops trigger cortisol\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 322.6 Td (- Take a genuine break \(walk outside, not scrolling\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 308.6 Td (- 10-minute breathwork or meditation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 294.6 Td (- Set a hard stop time for work) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 276.6 Td (Evening \(Lower cortisol for sleep\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 260.6 Td (- Dim lights after sunset) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 246.6 Td (- No screens 1+ hour before bed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 232.6 Td (- Magnesium supplement \(glycinate\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 218.6 Td (- Journaling or brain dump \(externalize worries\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 204.6 Td (- Calming tea: chamomile, lemon balm, valerian) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 190.6 Td (- Restorative yoga or gentle stretching) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 160.8 Td (Immediate Stress Reset Techniques) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 142.8 Td (- Physiological sigh: Double inhale, long exhale \(30 seconds\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 128.8 Td (- Cold water on face or wrists \(vagal nerve activation\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 114.8 Td (- 5-4-3-2-1 grounding \(senses check\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 100.8 Td (- Progressive muscle relaxation \(2 minutes\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 86.8 Td (- Walk outside for 5 minutes \(nature + movement\)) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
