stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 5: Recovery Nutrition & Sleep) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Eating for Burnout Recovery) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (Burnout depletes nutrients. Your body needs replenishment, not restriction.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 628.4 Td (Key Nutrients for Recovery) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 612.4 Td (- Magnesium: Depleted by stress \(leafy greens, dark chocolate, nuts\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 598.4 Td (- B vitamins: Used rapidly during stress \(whole grains, eggs, meat\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 584.4 Td (- Vitamin C: Adrenal support \(citrus, bell peppers, berries\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 570.4 Td (- Omega-3: Brain repair and anti-inflammatory \(fatty fish, walnuts\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 556.4 Td (- Protein: Neurotransmitter building blocks \(every meal\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 542.4 Td (- Complex carbs: Serotonin production \(sweet potato, oats\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 514.6 Td (Eating Principles for Recovery) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 498.6 Td (- Eat within 1 hour of waking \(stabilize cortisol\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 484.6 Td (- Don't skip meals \(blood sugar crashes worsen burnout\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 470.6 Td (- Protein at every meal \(brain chemistry support\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 456.6 Td (- Reduce caffeine \(further depletes adrenals\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 442.6 Td (- Reduce sugar \(energy rollercoaster\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 428.6 Td (- Hydrate well \(dehydration mimics fatigue\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 398.8 Td (Sleep Recovery Protocol) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 380.8 Td (Sleep is when your body repairs from stress. It is NON-NEGOTIABLE for recovery.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 366.8 Td (- Target: 8-9 hours \(more than usual - you're healing\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 352.8 Td (- Consistent schedule \(same time daily, even weekends\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 338.8 Td (- Wind-down routine starting 90 minutes before bed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 324.8 Td (- No work in the bedroom \(retrain brain\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 310.8 Td (- Magnesium glycinate before bed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 296.8 Td (- If racing mind: Write a brain dump list, then close the notebook) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 282.8 Td (- If can't sleep: Get up after 20 min, do something boring, return when sleepy) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
