100 0 obj
<< /Length 3026 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Frequently Asked Questions) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Q: How long does burnout recovery take?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (Full recovery typically takes 3-12 months with significant lifestyle changes. Some people) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (need longer. It depends on severity, how long you've been burned out, and what changes you) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.2 Td (make. Be patient.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 604.4 Td (Q: Should I quit my job?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (Not necessarily immediately. First try: setting boundaries, reducing hours, changing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 574.4 Td (responsibilities, or taking medical leave. If the environment is fundamentally toxic and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 560.4 Td (change isn't possible, leaving may be necessary for your health.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 532.6 Td (Q: Is burnout a medical condition?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 516.6 Td (The WHO classifies burnout as an occupational phenomenon \(not a medical diagnosis\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 502.6 Td (However, it can cause or worsen medical conditions \(depression, anxiety, cardiovascular) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 488.6 Td (disease\). Seek medical care if needed.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 460.8 Td (Q: Why can't I just push through?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 444.8 Td (Burnout is a nervous system state, not a motivation problem. 'Pushing through' is what) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 430.8 Td (caused burnout in the first place. Recovery requires doing LESS, not more. Rest is not) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 416.8 Td (laziness - it's medicine.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 389.0 Td (Q: Will exercise help or hurt?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 373.0 Td (Gentle exercise \(walking, yoga, swimming\) helps recovery. Intense exercise can worsen) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 359.0 Td (burnout by adding physical stress to an already-overwhelmed system. Start gentle, increase) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 345.0 Td (only when energy improves.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 317.2 Td (Q: How do I explain burnout to others?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 301.2 Td (You might say: 'I've been running on empty for too long and my body and mind need rest to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 287.2 Td (recover. This is a health issue, not a choice or weakness.' You don't owe anyone a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 273.2 Td (detailed explanation.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 245.4 Td (Q: Can burnout come back?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 229.4 Td (Yes, if you return to the same patterns. Recovery must include systemic changes: better) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 215.4 Td (boundaries, realistic expectations, regular rest, and addressing root causes. Prevention) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 201.4 Td (is ongoing.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 173.6 Td (Q: When should I seek professional help?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 157.6 Td (Immediately if: you have thoughts of self-harm, you cannot function \(work, self-care,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 143.6 Td (relationships\), symptoms of depression persist, or you've tried self-help for 4-6 weeks) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 129.6 Td (without improvement.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
